    "In contrast, the model's performance appears to decrease when a contrastive hint is introduced.",
    "This observed pattern brings into question the pragmatic abilities of these models, suggesting that their understanding and interpretation of language may be more significantly influenced by the presence and nature of linguistic cues than by inherent logic.",
    "Does a Model's Scale Correlate with Its Pragmatic Abilities?",
